text:
The New viral Starbucks Bearista glass cup sold out so quickly, the Company has issued a statement saying there will be a second drop of the Holiday Christmas Collection coming in December. They are doing everything they can to Restock the besrista Cup.  no promises yet.  but if they were to Restock I will post.
It will be one of two things they can do. 1. The announce it before hand a certain release date. this can help to boost the stocks, but will cause many people to have to wait in lines at 4am.  2. each store will put them out randomly as they get them.
Some store employees already see the bearista cup in the up coming future orders.  they are not allowed to tell us when.  and no pre-orders ever.

follow @magicalsoulfoodie to see more posts like this and to get updates when i post them.

authorMeta.name: margieslifeinelyu
text: Replying to @titades kapag o-order ka, simple lang—sabihin mo lang sa barista kung anong drink yung gusto mo. Pwede mong sabihin kung hot or iced, o kung may specific flavor ka na trip. Kung may part ka na di ka sure, don’t worry kasi nandiyan naman yung mga barista para mag-guide at sumagot ng questions mo. Usually, they can also recommend best-sellers or help ka mag-customize ng inumin ayon sa taste mo. Ang importante talaga is maging confident ka lang when ordering—kahit first time mo, sanay na sila tumulong sa customers, and they’ll appreciate na nag-try ka. Eventually, masasanay ka rin at magiging mas fun yung experience!:))) #starbucksdrinks #starbuckselyu #starbucksmenu
